{"tid":1943080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】英國王儲查理斯王子確診　太太卡米拉未有發現病毒","createTime":"2020-03-25T12:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T12:43:59.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0be47281d929485cfd65d563b3cf0ad6df94b721","tid":1943080,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200325-11_ytBBH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200325-11_ytBBH_1200x0.png&h=9debf474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國天空新聞報道引述克拉倫斯宮聲明，指王儲查理斯王子接受武漢肺炎檢測，證實為陽性，但除此之外仍然健康。報道又指，查理斯王子正與現任太太卡米拉在蘇格蘭自我隔離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181109/ee901114be5c46618ce20957ca4e0d91.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181109%2Fee901114be5c46618ce20957ca4e0d91.jpeg&h=5b77ab6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據《BBC》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">查理斯現任太太卡米拉亦有進行病毒測試，但未有發現病毒（</span> does not have the virus）。報道引述官方聲明，由於查理斯過去幾周擔任的公職眾多，因此暫時未能確認如何感染病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1s12pfo/ctp-vzntr/1533113136174911721r0n4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1s12pfo%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1533113136174911721r0n4.jpg&h=3d4fc389&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abd629d33ea0be7df645a415ecaf9caec0a1c3b0","tid":1943080,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有古怪"},{"pid":"09afaf8fdbc518372a37145b2795292baec17733","tid":1943080,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街又出去滾</span>"},{"pid":"508b7806de0200076a2809ea9d9a5b516482b85f","tid":1943080,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"未來幾日邊個確診係關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e752be468679bfbe5ead6c4eba649ed691557","tid":1943080,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"後生女同"}]}